WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:02.351
<i>Previously on "Somewhere Between"...</i>

00:02.716 --> 00:04.781
LAURA: This is the man who took Serena.

00:04.843 --> 00:06.076
SARNEAU: What about the safety pin?

00:06.101 --> 00:07.273
It was caught in her sweater.

00:07.336 --> 00:09.945
Come out and show yourself, Serena,

00:10.039 --> 00:11.617
or it will end badly for your friend.

00:11.656 --> 00:13.755
Stop!

00:13.780 --> 00:15.992
You better keep your promise.

00:16.094 --> 00:18.360
We can work something out
once I'm in office.

00:18.361 --> 00:19.194
[GUNSHOT]

00:19.195 --> 00:21.493
[GASPS]

00:21.494 --> 00:22.793
To the client. Fast.

00:22.794 --> 00:24.660
Mrs. Jackson, it is out of the question

00:24.661 --> 00:26.626
for you to leave this hospital
in your condition.

00:26.627 --> 00:27.993
You want my son to die alone?

00:27.994 --> 00:31.360
For my last meal, I want oatmeal.

00:31.361 --> 00:33.293
Captain Nico would've
hung your ass up to dry.

00:33.294 --> 00:34.460
Does your mother know
you talk like that?

00:34.461 --> 00:36.360
Does your mother know
you kidnap little girls?

00:36.361 --> 00:38.693
We have the jewelry,
and we have the girl,

00:38.694 --> 00:41.293
So nothing... is ever gonna hurt you.

00:41.294 --> 00:43.893
That's... That's Logan Dekizer.
That's the governor's son.

00:43.894 --> 00:46.226
Not the foster son. Blood.

00:46.227 --> 00:49.160
Richard Ruskin has no idea
what's headed for him.

00:49.161 --> 00:51.560
[TIRES SQUEAL]

00:51.561 --> 00:53.460
What can we expect at Ruskin's place?

00:53.461 --> 00:54.926
Dogs? Armed guards?

00:54.927 --> 00:56.793
Carmen. Housekeeper.

00:56.794 --> 00:58.969
She makes tamales for us
every Christmas.

00:59.431 --> 01:01.493
LOGAN: The karate lessons, the lullaby.

01:01.494 --> 01:03.093
If this comes to
what it may well come to,

01:03.094 --> 01:04.160
c-can he do it?

01:04.161 --> 01:05.626
You know what he's done for us
this week.

01:05.627 --> 01:07.660
He shot a man that killed 10 women,

01:07.661 --> 01:10.226
not some kid he's playing house with.

01:10.227 --> 01:11.626
She needs to be somewhere else.

01:11.627 --> 01:14.060
He came to us troubled and alone.

01:14.061 --> 01:15.960
Everything we did for him
never changed that.

01:15.961 --> 01:19.693
I want him to feel loved and trusted.

01:19.694 --> 01:21.328
He faked his own death

01:21.464 --> 01:23.697
- to get away from us.
- He came back.

01:23.761 --> 01:27.984
You hunted him down, and...
and you dragged him back.

01:28.427 --> 01:29.826
Let me go there myself.

01:29.827 --> 01:30.993
I'll take her to the boat.

01:30.994 --> 01:32.360
It's too much risk.

01:32.361 --> 01:34.593
Then call Ruskin and have
one of his spooks do it.

01:34.594 --> 01:38.026
♪♪

01:38.027 --> 01:39.226
[GRUNTS]

01:39.227 --> 01:42.702
Mom, I will not let them take me
to prison alive.

01:42.875 --> 01:45.440
I'm telling you that right now.

01:45.527 --> 01:49.526
[VOICE BREAKING]
I will take myself out so fast.

01:49.527 --> 01:52.193
♪♪

01:52.194 --> 01:54.076
All right.

01:54.192 --> 01:55.658
All right.

01:55.761 --> 01:57.576
I'll call Ruskin.

01:57.982 --> 02:03.836
