17:29.041 --> 17:31.540
[GRUNTS]

17:31.541 --> 17:40.740
♪♪

17:40.741 --> 17:42.574
[GRUNTS]

17:42.575 --> 17:52.540
♪♪

17:52.541 --> 18:02.540
♪♪

18:02.541 --> 18:12.540
♪♪

18:12.607 --> 18:14.206
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

18:14.207 --> 18:16.706
[KEYPAD BEEPS]

18:16.737 --> 18:18.028
[SIGHS]

18:18.053 --> 18:19.485
<i>Don't call the police.</i>

18:19.510 --> 18:21.076
<i>Right now, we can't trust them.</i>

18:21.077 --> 18:23.376
Oh, Mom!

18:23.377 --> 18:26.442
What's your number? It was in my phone!

18:26.443 --> 18:28.142
What's Dad's?

18:28.143 --> 18:30.276
RUBY: <i>And it's super-easy to remember</i>

18:30.277 --> 18:32.509
<i>'cause the first three numbers
are all the same,</i>

18:32.510 --> 18:34.509
<i>and the last four spell out "cool."</i>

18:34.510 --> 18:36.509
<i>C-O-O-L.</i>

18:36.510 --> 18:39.042
[BEEPING]

18:39.043 --> 18:41.142
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

18:41.143 --> 18:43.142
[BEEP]

18:43.143 --> 18:45.509
- Hello?
- SERENA: <i> Ruby, it's me!</i>

18:45.510 --> 18:49.218
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!
Grandma, it's Serena!

18:49.710 --> 18:51.609
Honey, where are you? Are you all right?

18:51.610 --> 18:53.009
<i>This man kidnapped me.</i>

18:53.010 --> 18:55.076
But he wasn't bad. He was just sad.

18:55.077 --> 18:56.376
And the governor's wife came,

18:56.377 --> 18:57.676
<i>and her son killed him...</i>

18:57.677 --> 18:59.742
Wait, wait, wait. The governor's wife?

18:59.743 --> 19:01.142
Y-Y-You're not making any sense.

19:01.143 --> 19:02.576
No! That's who it was.

19:02.577 --> 19:04.709
They took me away, but I escaped.

19:04.710 --> 19:06.176
I couldn't remember anyone's number

19:06.177 --> 19:07.809
except yours because I just learned it,

19:07.810 --> 19:09.409
<i>and my mom told me not
to call the police!</i>

19:09.410 --> 19:11.342
- Where are you?
- Um...

19:11.343 --> 19:13.076
I can see this big waterfall.

19:13.077 --> 19:14.609
I went there on a picnic once.

19:14.610 --> 19:15.577
Echo Falls.

19:15.578 --> 19:17.176
I know where that is.

19:17.177 --> 19:18.576
Are you on a road?

19:18.577 --> 19:19.709
Dirt road.

19:19.710 --> 19:21.009
<i>We'll be there as soon as we can.</i>

19:21.010 --> 19:22.109
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

19:22.110 --> 19:25.309
NICO: All those guys
for all those years...

19:25.310 --> 19:26.277
nobody broke?

19:26.278 --> 19:28.176
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]
- Huh?

19:28.177 --> 19:30.209
Why did they keep the secret?

19:30.210 --> 19:32.483
Money?

19:32.843 --> 19:35.676
Blake wanted to call 911.

19:35.677 --> 19:37.242
[ <i>CELLPHONE BEEPS</i> ]

19:37.243 --> 19:39.076
<i>What are you doing?</i>

19:39.077 --> 19:40.509
<i>Saving her life.</i>

19:40.510 --> 19:42.109
<i>So she can testify against us?</i>

19:42.110 --> 19:43.842
<i>I didn't do anything to her.</i>

19:43.843 --> 19:44.843
<i>I tried to save her.</i>

19:44.844 --> 19:46.309
<i>That's the story you'll tell.</i>

19:46.310 --> 19:48.110
<i>- Wait'll you hear mine.
- You son of a bitch!</i>

19:48.111 --> 19:49.876
<i>Hey! Down.</i>

19:49.877 --> 19:51.709
<i>Yeah, sure, call 911.</i>

19:51.710 --> 19:53.242
<i>Bring the cops.</i>

19:53.243 --> 19:54.742
<i>And while every channel on TV</i>

19:54.743 --> 19:56.676
<i>is hashing out whose story is true,</i>

19:56.677 --> 19:58.561
<i>you think that A&R guy
from Warner Records</i>

19:58.586 --> 20:00.352
<i>is gonna keep sniffing around you? Huh?</i>

20:00.377 --> 20:01.776
<i>You...</i>

20:01.777 --> 20:04.842
<i>You think you're all set,
heading for USC film.</i>

20:04.977 --> 20:07.542
<i>You know how fast they can rescind?</i>

20:07.543 --> 20:10.309
<i>End of your bromance with
that scout from the Raiders.</i>

20:10.310 --> 20:12.610
<i>So you can call 911.</i>

20:13.777 --> 20:16.047
<i>Or I can make this whole thing go away</i>

20:16.277 --> 20:17.642
<i>like it never happened.</i>

20:17.855 --> 20:20.063
Logan made the call he made every time.

20:20.210 --> 20:21.709
Every time he killed somebody?

20:21.710 --> 20:24.076
Before that, it was never a dead girl.

20:24.077 --> 20:25.842
Just broken ones.

20:25.843 --> 20:27.342
<i>Listen, I'm gonna need your help.</i>

20:27.343 --> 20:29.209
<i>Things here got a little screwed up.</i>

20:29.711 --> 20:31.642
<i>I don't know, on a scale
between smashing a fender</i>

20:31.643 --> 20:34.680
<i>and running a bus full of
disabled children off a cliff?</i>

20:35.077 --> 20:36.476
<i>I'd say right in the middle.</i>

20:36.477 --> 20:39.076
KYLE: 45 minutes later, a limo pulls up

20:39.077 --> 20:40.967
and Richard Ruskin got out...

20:41.110 --> 20:43.061
the family fixer.

20:43.277 --> 20:45.276
<i>This is how it's gonna go.</i>

20:45.277 --> 20:47.776
<i>You know the reach and
influence of Logan's family.</i>

20:47.777 --> 20:49.576
<i>You know the mess they can
make of your futures,</i>

20:49.577 --> 20:51.109
<i>so do exactly as I say.</i>

20:53.043 --> 20:55.367
He made us all stab her three times.

20:55.610 --> 20:58.492
He filmed it on his phone.

20:58.577 --> 21:01.592
- <i>Get down there!</i>
- She was alive till Ruskin got there.

21:01.756 --> 21:04.568
One of us killed her.

21:05.043 --> 21:06.609
Or all of us.

21:06.610 --> 21:09.276
♪♪

21:09.277 --> 21:11.437
When it was over...

21:11.843 --> 21:14.476
when it was time to set the fire,

21:14.477 --> 21:16.042
Logan and I got called outside.

21:16.043 --> 21:18.109
<i>Thank you.</i>

21:18.377 --> 21:21.034
<i>Thank you and bless you.</i>

21:21.477 --> 21:25.309
It was my job to destroy
the card from Blake's camera.

21:25.310 --> 21:27.955
So I threw it in the fire
in front of everybody.

21:28.110 --> 21:31.109
But growing up on the streets,
you get good at sleight-of-hand.

21:31.110 --> 21:32.776
Why'd you keep it?

21:33.262 --> 21:35.309
- For today.
- Like Jesse kept the scarf.

21:35.310 --> 21:36.909
Is that what he brought your husband?

21:36.910 --> 21:38.809
I guess he couldn't live
with himself anymore.

21:38.810 --> 21:40.328
Apparently, you could.

21:40.353 --> 21:43.052
I joined the Air Force the next day,

21:43.077 --> 21:45.109
requested the Gulf.

21:45.110 --> 21:47.176
A lot of fliers died who shouldn't have.

21:47.177 --> 21:49.109
I should've and didn't.

21:49.110 --> 21:51.809
You became a ghost.

21:52.215 --> 21:54.676
The better to serve your master.

21:54.677 --> 21:55.942
Better to be done with them.

21:55.943 --> 21:57.676
Yeah, big moral outrage.

21:57.677 --> 21:59.324
But letting my brother die,

21:59.410 --> 22:01.706
- that didn't ruffle any feathers, huh?
- Nico, wait!

22:01.787 --> 22:03.586
Wait until he saves Serena and Danny.

22:03.610 --> 22:05.442
Then you can do whatever
you want with him.

22:05.443 --> 22:07.076
♪♪

22:07.077 --> 22:09.742
[COUGHS]

22:09.743 --> 22:11.210
♪♪

22:15.596 --> 22:18.158
Serena!

22:18.183 --> 22:19.282
[CAR APPROACHING]

22:19.307 --> 22:21.148
Serena!

22:21.491 --> 22:23.325
Oh, my gosh, I'm here!

22:27.820 --> 22:29.086
Gosh, thank you for coming!

22:29.115 --> 22:30.647
Of course!

22:30.672 --> 22:33.371
We have to get back to the jail
so my dad isn't alone.

22:33.420 --> 22:34.571
Yes.

22:34.596 --> 22:37.395
But first, we have
to let Serena's dad know

22:37.420 --> 22:38.686
that she's okay.

22:38.687 --> 22:40.419
<i>That's my cellphone.</i>

22:40.420 --> 22:42.119
<i>If you hear from her,
please let me know?</i>

22:42.120 --> 22:43.061
SERENA: I want to talk to him!

22:43.086 --> 22:45.418
I don't have his number,
but I-I can... I can get him.

22:45.687 --> 22:48.853
I just have to text somebody.

22:48.854 --> 22:51.519
[GIRLS TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

22:51.520 --> 22:52.857
[CELLPHONE BUTTONS CLICKING]

22:52.893 --> 22:56.893
_

22:58.361 --> 22:59.527
Richard!

22:59.654 --> 23:06.919
♪♪

23:06.920 --> 23:08.862
Richard?!

23:08.958 --> 23:10.223
Carmen?!

23:10.420 --> 23:11.954
[RUSKIN GROANING]

23:16.095 --> 23:17.260
Nico and Laura did this.

23:17.261 --> 23:19.136
- Oh, my God.
- They tied me. I can't move.

23:19.161 --> 23:20.194
Oh, my God!

23:20.195 --> 23:21.994
Get help.

23:21.995 --> 23:23.960
- [SIGHS]
- [CELLPHONE BEEPING]

23:23.961 --> 23:25.127
[RINGING]

23:25.128 --> 23:27.873
They know Logan killed Susanna.

23:28.428 --> 23:31.592
They demanded to know where Serena is.

23:32.352 --> 23:35.094
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

23:35.119 --> 23:36.754
And you told them?

23:36.861 --> 23:38.360
[VOICE BREAKING]
Look what they did to me.

23:38.361 --> 23:39.927
They took my fingers!

23:40.207 --> 23:42.582
Luckily, Logan and I got there first.

23:42.761 --> 23:45.494
[SIGHS]

23:45.495 --> 23:46.827
Give me Laura's number.

23:46.828 --> 23:49.160
If I can get control of her,
then I'll call for help for you.

23:49.161 --> 23:51.094
It's in my phone, but they took it.

23:51.095 --> 23:51.961
[EXHALES SHARPLY]

23:51.962 --> 23:53.394
But I have Tom's phone.

23:53.395 --> 23:54.594
It's in the drawer.

23:54.595 --> 23:56.887
Her number must be in it.

23:58.128 --> 24:00.494
Someone's been trying
to text him for a half hour.

24:00.495 --> 24:02.428
Get help!

24:02.918 --> 24:04.502
_

24:04.527 --> 24:06.660
How can Grace Jackson have Serena?

24:06.661 --> 24:07.927
Logan took her.

24:07.928 --> 24:09.494
Colleen, please!

24:09.495 --> 24:10.560
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

24:10.561 --> 24:11.894
[RINGING]

24:11.895 --> 24:13.528
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

24:15.710 --> 24:17.776
Uh... let's not answer that.

24:17.895 --> 24:19.494
She may figure out where we are.

24:19.495 --> 24:20.461
- [CELLPHONE BEEPS]
- [EXHALES SHARPLY]

24:20.462 --> 24:22.901
Logan, call me.

24:23.361 --> 24:25.298
Colleen, get me some help!

24:25.761 --> 24:27.627
[EXHALES SHARPLY]

24:27.652 --> 24:30.380
[CELLPHONE BUZZES]

24:30.405 --> 24:31.614
_

24:31.695 --> 24:33.395
[GIRLS TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

24:34.526 --> 24:37.213
_

24:37.261 --> 24:39.295
[SIGHS]

24:40.728 --> 24:42.261
[CELLPHONE VIBRATES]

24:42.480 --> 24:45.103
_

24:50.861 --> 24:52.394
[CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS, PHONE VIBRATES]

24:52.395 --> 24:54.228
[SIGHS]

24:55.728 --> 24:59.260
♪♪

24:59.261 --> 25:00.461
Okay.

25:02.270 --> 25:05.824
_

25:06.761 --> 25:08.494
Get my dad's number yet?

25:08.495 --> 25:10.627
[CHUCKLES] He's on his way.

25:10.628 --> 25:11.595
He's coming.

25:11.596 --> 25:13.194
Okay.

25:13.195 --> 25:15.827
- [CELLPHONE BEEPS, RINGS]
- Colleen, I'm gonna bleed to death here!

25:15.828 --> 25:18.627
When my son is completely
and permanently safe,

25:18.628 --> 25:20.994
I'll send for help.

25:20.995 --> 25:22.508
Setsuko.

25:22.616 --> 25:25.981
I need the chopper
at the downtown heliport.

25:26.061 --> 25:27.894
As soon as possible.

25:27.895 --> 25:38.294
♪♪

25:38.295 --> 25:48.694
♪♪

25:48.695 --> 25:59.127
♪♪

25:59.128 --> 26:00.495
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

26:05.161 --> 26:07.327
[SEATBELT UNBUCKLES]

26:07.328 --> 26:09.094
[GRUNTING]

26:09.095 --> 26:18.727
♪♪

26:18.728 --> 26:28.394
♪♪

26:28.395 --> 26:30.394
- What's the problem?
- Get out.

26:30.395 --> 26:31.861
Get out!

26:35.195 --> 26:36.895
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

26:42.628 --> 26:45.127
[SHOUTING CONTINUES]

26:45.128 --> 26:47.661
[VEHICLE DOORS OPEN]

26:49.195 --> 26:52.007
DEKIZER:
<i>The first of the three drugs in the trio</i>

26:52.095 --> 26:54.327
- <i>guarantees absence of pain...</i>
- LAURA: Aaron.

26:54.366 --> 26:56.101
- <i>...as the remaining drugs take effect.</i>
- Laura!

26:56.161 --> 26:57.627
Is there a screen in there? A TV?

26:57.628 --> 26:59.612
It's the board room, yeah,
so there's a screen.

26:59.637 --> 27:01.203
- What's going on?
- We're going in.

27:01.228 --> 27:03.946
You won't get him in there...
Security's off the charts.

27:04.028 --> 27:05.960
Without credentials, there's no way.

27:05.961 --> 27:07.360
What are you gonna do?

27:08.063 --> 27:10.361
Blow up the world.

27:13.288 --> 27:15.155
Is there time to see your brother?

27:15.233 --> 27:17.665
He's already in the works,
but I know I'll see him again.

27:17.666 --> 27:18.620
How?

27:19.910 --> 27:21.743
Because his fate's in your hands.

27:21.768 --> 27:24.658
♪♪

27:26.104 --> 27:27.665
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

27:27.690 --> 27:29.064
- [CELLPHONE BEEPS]
- Hey, Ma.

27:29.089 --> 27:30.202
We're close.

27:30.227 --> 27:31.588
Laura's going in right now to...

27:31.613 --> 27:32.972
GRACE: <i> Nico, it's over.</i>

27:32.997 --> 27:35.563
The DA told me
he's reopening Danny's case.

27:36.254 --> 27:37.797
Which DA?

27:37.848 --> 27:39.847
[CHUCKLING] Tom Price, who do you think?

27:39.848 --> 27:41.714
Oh, and I-I-I have Serena.

27:41.715 --> 27:43.114
<i>She's safe. She's with me.</i>

27:43.115 --> 27:44.433
Mom, ho... hold on one second.

27:44.458 --> 27:45.690
Hey! Laura, hey!

27:45.715 --> 27:47.722
- Come here!
- What?

27:47.901 --> 27:49.643
- What? What is it?
- My mom has Serena.

27:49.715 --> 27:51.047
- [CELLPHONE BEEPS]
- What?

27:51.048 --> 27:52.081
[CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

27:52.082 --> 27:53.462
Mom, how did you talk to Tom Price?

27:53.511 --> 27:54.876
Not talk, texted.

27:54.948 --> 27:56.047
Mom, the DA's dead.

27:56.048 --> 27:57.647
The people that killed him
have his phone.

27:57.648 --> 27:58.847
<i>Did you tell him where you are?</i>

27:58.872 --> 28:00.697
<i>- Did you tell them where Serena is?</i>
- Yes.

28:00.722 --> 28:02.490
- [SIGHS]
- Where are you, Mom?

28:02.515 --> 28:05.715
On a fire road off Route 1,

28:05.801 --> 28:07.745
- <i>near Echo Falls.</i>
- Nico...

28:07.746 --> 28:09.567
Okay, you have to get out of there
right now, really fast, okay?

28:09.568 --> 28:10.754
<i>Stay on the fire road.</i>

28:10.801 --> 28:11.833
Don't go to the highway.

28:11.834 --> 28:13.467
I'm going to track you with your phone.

28:13.468 --> 28:15.634
<i>- Go! Now!</i>
- Oh, God.

28:15.635 --> 28:18.500
Girls, get in the car. We're leaving.

28:18.501 --> 28:20.567
How's my dad supposed to find us?

28:20.568 --> 28:21.933
We'll call him when
we get to where we're going,

28:21.934 --> 28:24.554
but we have to leave right away.

28:24.801 --> 28:26.867
The other side of the hill
from Echo Falls

28:26.868 --> 28:28.633
is Black Pine Cove.

28:28.634 --> 28:29.733
It's not too late.

28:29.734 --> 28:31.467
W-W-We can meet up with them
in 20 minutes.

28:31.468 --> 28:32.981
Not <i> me.</i>

28:33.601 --> 28:35.505
You.

28:36.544 --> 28:37.800
What are you talking about?

28:37.801 --> 28:39.867
I have to go in there. I can save Danny.

28:39.868 --> 28:43.326
If you go now, you can save them both.

28:43.525 --> 28:45.433
I'll borrow Aaron's car, and...

28:45.434 --> 28:47.467
and I'll meet you guys at the cove.

28:47.468 --> 28:49.693
♪♪

28:49.783 --> 28:51.772
You would stay here?

28:54.644 --> 28:57.180
[SCOFFS]

28:57.224 --> 28:58.690
I trust you.

28:58.801 --> 29:05.500
♪♪

29:05.501 --> 29:12.200
♪♪

29:12.201 --> 29:14.101
Go, okay?

29:15.468 --> 29:24.600
♪♪

29:24.601 --> 29:33.700
♪♪

29:33.701 --> 29:35.067
[GASPS]

29:35.068 --> 29:37.933
Somebody's coming!

29:37.934 --> 29:40.300
SERENA: It's him!
The man I got away from!

29:40.301 --> 29:43.168
[MONITOR BEEPING RHYTHMICALLY]

29:47.534 --> 29:50.400
DEKIZER: The question
of scripture and faith

29:50.401 --> 29:51.600
is a powerful one

29:51.601 --> 29:54.708
and, uh, I thank you for asking it.

29:54.768 --> 29:56.200
The Book of Numbers is clear

29:56.201 --> 29:58.067
both on the validity
of the death penalty

29:58.068 --> 30:01.733
and on the almost impossibly high bar...

30:01.734 --> 30:02.967
Governor Dekizer...

30:02.968 --> 30:04.667
Excuse me, Ms. Price,

30:04.668 --> 30:06.400
if you would allow me to finish?

30:06.401 --> 30:08.500
Governor, do you have
absolutely no doubt

30:08.525 --> 30:10.145
that Danny Jackson is guilty

30:10.170 --> 30:11.833
of the murder of Susanna Spencer?

30:11.834 --> 30:13.467
Well, first of all, I want you to know

30:13.468 --> 30:15.367
that law enforcement
is moving heaven and earth

30:15.368 --> 30:16.368
to find your daughter.

30:16.369 --> 30:18.633
I'm not asking about Serena.

30:18.634 --> 30:20.433
I want to know, do you have any doubt

30:20.434 --> 30:22.733
that Danny Jackson killed
Susanna Spencer?

30:22.734 --> 30:24.833
Over the decade since the conviction,

30:24.834 --> 30:26.933
every possible doubt has been explored

30:26.934 --> 30:28.967
by a painstaking process of appeals.

30:28.968 --> 30:30.900
Those appeals haven't taken into account

30:30.925 --> 30:33.843
the new evidence,
which is in the hands of KMSF.

30:33.868 --> 30:35.833
AIDE: Mrs. Price,
if there's evidence relevant

30:35.834 --> 30:37.800
<i>to the Jackson case,
we encourage you to present it</i>

30:37.801 --> 30:39.533
<i>through the appropriate legal channels.</i>

30:39.534 --> 30:41.367
<i>With Danny Jackson scheduled
to be murdered</i>

30:41.368 --> 30:42.958
<i>by the State of California</i>

30:42.982 --> 30:44.222
in 12 minutes,

30:44.223 --> 30:46.000
this is the only channel I've got.

30:46.001 --> 30:48.433
That's fine, but...
Where did you get this evidence?

30:48.434 --> 30:50.450
- Your foster son.
- Excuse me?

30:50.534 --> 30:54.731
<i>Governor, we are broadcasting
this evidence now, live,</i>

30:54.801 --> 30:56.467
<i>and we wanted to give you an opportunity</i>

30:56.468 --> 30:58.367
to respond to the news as it's breaking.

30:58.368 --> 31:00.033
- Turn on the TV, please.
- I... I'm sorry.

31:00.034 --> 31:01.367
This is completely out of order,

31:01.368 --> 31:03.734
- Governor, and we don't...
- Wait. I want to see this.

31:03.968 --> 31:05.633
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

31:05.634 --> 31:07.467
Run it now. Split the screen.

31:07.468 --> 31:09.300
LOGAN: <i>It's no fair pulling it back.</i>

31:09.301 --> 31:10.800
SUSANNA: <i> Get off me!</i>

31:10.801 --> 31:13.106
<i>- Oh, bitch wants to have fun, huh?!</i>
- [ <i>SCREAMS</i> ]

31:13.168 --> 31:14.633
[INDISTINCT MURMURING]

31:14.634 --> 31:16.200
[ <i>CHOKING</i> ]

31:16.201 --> 31:17.633
[GASPS]

31:17.634 --> 31:18.867
[ <i>INDISTINCT SHOUTING</i> ]

31:18.868 --> 31:21.001
Governor, is that your son?
Is that Logan?

31:24.168 --> 31:25.367
JESSE: <i> Logan, no!</i>

31:25.368 --> 31:27.100
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

31:27.101 --> 31:30.567
Governor, I demand you issue
a stay of execution

31:30.568 --> 31:32.314
while you verify the tape.

31:32.468 --> 31:34.143
Will you issue the stay?

31:34.751 --> 31:36.100
Yes. Yes.

31:36.101 --> 31:37.767
[SCREAMS]

31:37.768 --> 31:39.233
<i>This is an executive order...</i>

31:39.234 --> 31:41.400
<i>halt the execution of Danny Jackson.</i>

31:41.401 --> 31:42.533
<i>Halt it!</i>

31:42.534 --> 31:44.534
You got mine.

31:45.228 --> 31:46.993
I'm gonna get yours.

31:47.018 --> 31:48.117
[ENGINE REVS]

31:48.142 --> 31:51.381
Governor, is it true that my husband,

31:51.434 --> 31:53.233
Thomas Price, knew the truth

31:53.491 --> 31:55.514
and that you kidnapped my daughter

31:55.625 --> 31:56.967
to force him to keep it a secret?

31:56.968 --> 31:58.267
- Okay, Mrs. Price, this is enough...
- No. No.

31:58.268 --> 31:59.500
- This is enough, Governor.
- No! No!

31:59.501 --> 32:02.134
I-I never... That's not the truth.

32:02.135 --> 32:03.200
That's not... that's not my son.

32:03.201 --> 32:04.976
I told you.

32:05.501 --> 32:06.667
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

32:06.668 --> 32:07.534
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

32:07.535 --> 32:08.567
Nico, where are you?

32:08.568 --> 32:10.100
- You watching?
- You kidding?

32:10.101 --> 32:11.633
<i>The Dekizers are after Serena.</i>

32:11.634 --> 32:13.300
<i>If they don't already have her.</i>

32:13.301 --> 32:15.033
They're headed to Black Pine Cove.

32:15.034 --> 32:17.468
Oh, I'll make sure to send
everything we've got.

32:22.901 --> 32:24.300
Get out of the car.

32:24.301 --> 32:25.867
We have to run and get help,

32:25.868 --> 32:27.133
as fast as we can.

32:27.134 --> 32:28.755
You can't run, Grandma!

32:28.901 --> 32:31.731
The doctor said you shouldn't do
anything hard!

32:31.744 --> 32:33.243
Doctors don't know everything!

32:33.268 --> 32:34.544
Come on!

32:34.656 --> 32:36.208
Come on!

32:36.434 --> 32:37.933
[TIRES SQUEALING]

32:37.958 --> 32:39.325
[TIRES SCREECH]

32:43.234 --> 32:45.067
[CAR DOOR CLOSES]

32:45.068 --> 32:46.733
Can somebody take my car?!

32:46.734 --> 32:48.133
LOGAN: <i>Bitch wants to have fun?!</i>

32:48.134 --> 32:50.300
REPORTER: <i>Breaking news...
highly graphic footage</i>

32:50.301 --> 32:53.167
<i>was broadcast
on live television moments ago</i>

32:53.168 --> 32:55.867
<i>of Logan Dekizer,
Governor Dekizer's son,</i>

32:55.868 --> 32:57.933
<i>brutally murdering Susanna Spencer</i>

32:57.934 --> 32:59.233
- <i>10 years ago.</i>
- [SOBBING]

32:59.234 --> 33:09.133
♪♪

33:09.134 --> 33:10.733
COLLEEN: I'm coming for you, Logan,

33:10.734 --> 33:11.992
to take you away,

33:12.134 --> 33:14.328
to where no one can ever touch you.

33:15.406 --> 33:17.038
Mama's coming!

33:17.101 --> 33:18.933
♪♪

33:18.934 --> 33:20.833
[BOTH PANTING]

33:20.834 --> 33:23.400
- There's the Bay!
- Bay means boat!

33:23.401 --> 33:24.867
Boats means people!

33:24.868 --> 33:26.433
I'll stay here and stand guard.

33:26.434 --> 33:27.933
You run and get help!

33:27.934 --> 33:31.000
- Grandma, are you okay?
- Go, go! Now!

33:31.001 --> 33:32.833
Okay.

33:32.834 --> 33:36.001
♪♪

33:41.075 --> 33:44.412
[CELLPHONE RINGING, BEEPS]

33:44.437 --> 33:45.521
You saved my brother's life!

33:45.607 --> 33:47.980
- Where are you?
- NICO: <i>I'm on the fire road!</i>

33:48.020 --> 33:49.118
I'm going over the hill!

33:49.119 --> 33:50.012
I'll take the coast.

33:50.052 --> 33:51.117
It's 15 minutes.

33:51.118 --> 33:57.784
♪♪

33:57.785 --> 34:01.350
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

34:01.351 --> 34:02.651
[GRUNTS]

34:04.918 --> 34:06.618
[BOTH GRUNTING]

34:08.167 --> 34:09.899
[CRYING]

34:09.900 --> 34:12.599
REPORTER: <i>Law enforcement reports
that no arrest has been made</i>

34:12.600 --> 34:14.766
<i>and that Logan Dekizer remains at large</i>

34:14.766 --> 34:16.766
<i>in the wake of an incendiary video,</i>

34:16.766 --> 34:20.000
<i>which has racked up over
30 million views and counting.</i>

34:21.632 --> 34:23.199
- Nico!
- Mom!

34:23.225 --> 34:24.308
- [MOANS]
- Hey.

34:24.333 --> 34:25.931
Hey, I'm gonna go get help!

34:25.933 --> 34:27.732
[WEAKLY] Help the girls.

34:27.733 --> 34:29.366
That way, to the cove!

34:29.367 --> 34:30.431
Mom...

34:30.433 --> 34:32.132
Danny's safe.

34:32.132 --> 34:33.766
The Governor halted the execution.

34:33.956 --> 34:36.370
Danny's going free!

34:37.333 --> 34:40.326
Then you don't have
to worry about me for a second.

34:40.748 --> 34:42.181
Save Serena.

34:42.181 --> 34:43.648
- Go! Go!
- I'll be back.

34:43.649 --> 34:45.315
I'll be back with help, okay?

34:45.340 --> 34:47.791
- Okay, Mom?
- Go! Hurry!

34:47.815 --> 34:50.848
♪♪

34:50.849 --> 34:51.947
RUBY: Help!

34:51.949 --> 34:54.081
- Help us!
- SERENA: Help! Help!

34:54.081 --> 34:56.012
Help us!

34:56.058 --> 34:57.224
- Please!
- Help!

34:57.249 --> 35:00.181
Please, help us!

35:00.182 --> 35:01.281
No more MMA!

35:01.282 --> 35:02.490
No!

35:02.515 --> 35:04.281
No! Serena!

35:04.282 --> 35:05.615
Come here, come here, come here.
Give me your hands.

35:05.616 --> 35:06.848
- Give me your hands.
- No!

35:06.873 --> 35:08.015
Hey! Stop it!

35:08.040 --> 35:09.700
No!

35:09.725 --> 35:11.270
- No!
- Don't be afraid.

35:11.295 --> 35:12.308
Don't be afraid, okay?

35:12.333 --> 35:13.448
- No!
- Okay?

35:13.449 --> 35:15.315
This is just so your mom
does the right thing.

35:15.316 --> 35:16.349
Ouch!

35:17.634 --> 35:19.167
[GRUNTS]

35:19.192 --> 35:21.291
Serena!

35:21.316 --> 35:22.481
[BOTH GRUNTING]

35:22.482 --> 35:23.548
I could kill you right now,

35:23.549 --> 35:24.848
but I want to see you
in my brother's cell.

35:24.849 --> 35:26.615
Everybody who could
put me there is dead.

35:26.616 --> 35:29.138
Oh, you didn't hear?

35:29.382 --> 35:31.388
Your brother never burnt the chip.

35:31.582 --> 35:33.481
That video's been around
the world twice by now.

35:33.513 --> 35:34.904
You...

35:35.016 --> 35:37.215
Susanna... the scarf.

35:37.216 --> 35:39.315
What is this, some kind of
pathetic bluff so I'll confess?

35:39.316 --> 35:41.747
"This must be your boyfriend's jacket.

35:41.816 --> 35:44.381
If I put it on, does that make
me your boyfriend?

35:44.382 --> 35:46.348
Oh, bitch wants to have fun!"

35:46.349 --> 35:47.808
[GRUNTS]

35:47.833 --> 35:50.915
♪♪

35:50.916 --> 35:52.981
[HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING]

35:52.982 --> 35:54.874
That's the cops!

35:55.062 --> 35:56.561
That's justice!

35:56.649 --> 35:59.215
♪♪

35:59.216 --> 36:00.348
No, it's not.

36:00.349 --> 36:01.481
That's freedom!

36:01.482 --> 36:08.500
♪♪

36:08.525 --> 36:15.557
♪♪

36:15.582 --> 36:22.123
♪♪

36:22.148 --> 36:26.115
Hey! Hey, hey! Serena, Ruby, run!

36:26.182 --> 36:27.616
Run!!

36:30.716 --> 36:33.481
♪♪

36:33.482 --> 36:34.915
SARNEAU: <i>What about the safety pin?</i>

36:34.916 --> 36:35.981
<i>It was caught on her sweater.</i>

36:35.982 --> 36:37.218
It was you...

36:37.316 --> 36:39.093
the first time.

36:39.316 --> 36:41.081
- You killed my baby.
- What?

36:41.082 --> 36:42.568
SERENA: Mom!

36:42.682 --> 36:46.981
Drop the gun and let him go,
or she goes in the water!

36:46.982 --> 36:48.315
Let her go!

36:49.255 --> 36:50.912
I will shoot him!

36:51.182 --> 36:53.388
We're the same, you and I!

36:53.482 --> 36:55.748
Everything that I did for my baby,

36:55.749 --> 36:58.048
you would do for yours if you had to!

36:58.049 --> 36:59.615
Let Serena go!

36:59.616 --> 37:01.414
My baby would never murder anyone!

37:01.482 --> 37:03.081
If she did, I'd let her pay!

37:03.082 --> 37:05.115
I said let her go!

37:05.116 --> 37:06.215
Ruby. Ruby!

37:06.216 --> 37:07.315
[GRUNTS]

37:07.316 --> 37:10.815
♪♪

37:10.816 --> 37:13.448
- Get away from me!
- My baby.

37:13.449 --> 37:14.748
You okay?

37:14.749 --> 37:16.415
Get away!

37:16.416 --> 37:19.291
- Logan! Make them pay!
- No!

37:19.316 --> 37:20.815
[SCREAMS]

37:20.816 --> 37:22.148
- [GUNSHOT]
- [GRUNTS]

37:22.149 --> 37:26.881
[SOUND DISTORTS]

37:26.882 --> 37:32.381
♪♪

37:32.382 --> 37:37.815
♪♪

37:37.816 --> 37:38.981
[SIRENS WAIL]

37:38.982 --> 37:40.248
COLLEEN: Logan, hurry!

37:40.249 --> 37:42.148
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

37:42.149 --> 37:43.893
Serena!

37:44.400 --> 37:45.830
Serena!

37:46.482 --> 37:48.338
Serena!

37:48.449 --> 37:55.881
♪♪

37:55.882 --> 38:03.348
♪♪

38:03.349 --> 38:10.815
♪♪

38:10.816 --> 38:18.281
♪♪

38:18.282 --> 38:25.715
♪♪

38:25.716 --> 38:27.916
[WAILING CONTINUES]

38:42.254 --> 38:44.081
- Serena!
- Ruby!

38:44.106 --> 38:45.167
Laura!

38:45.192 --> 38:47.524
[SERENA COUGHS]

38:47.549 --> 38:49.581
Uncle Nico!

38:49.582 --> 38:58.481
♪♪

38:58.482 --> 39:07.381
♪♪

39:07.382 --> 39:16.315
♪♪

39:16.316 --> 39:25.215
♪♪

39:25.802 --> 39:27.810
- [GASPING]
- Uncle Nico!

39:27.916 --> 39:29.318
Uncle Nico!

39:29.349 --> 39:30.781
Oh, my God!

39:30.782 --> 39:31.915
Oh, my God!

39:31.916 --> 39:40.381
♪♪

39:40.382 --> 39:42.581
[BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY]

39:42.906 --> 39:45.663
[WEAKLY] We always knew
fate wanted a body.

39:45.782 --> 39:48.976
She's getting a pretty good one,
if you ask me.

39:49.182 --> 39:51.218
You idiot.

39:51.416 --> 39:53.463
I love you.

39:53.564 --> 39:54.616
Hang in there.

39:54.697 --> 39:56.115
You sure?

39:56.116 --> 39:59.455
'Cause if I don't die,
you're stuck with me.

39:59.949 --> 40:04.148
♪♪

40:04.149 --> 40:05.719
Help!

40:05.982 --> 40:08.594
Help! Ruby, go get help!

40:08.849 --> 40:10.681
Help!!

40:10.682 --> 40:16.415
♪♪

40:16.416 --> 40:22.148
♪♪

40:22.298 --> 40:25.948
Javier, why are we flying east?

40:25.973 --> 40:27.281
I want to be out of Mexico

40:27.282 --> 40:29.767
and on the way to Honduras by tonight.

40:30.216 --> 40:31.679
We're flying too low.

40:31.781 --> 40:32.921
Javier, what's going on?

40:33.023 --> 40:34.081
[GROANING]

40:34.082 --> 40:40.248
♪♪

40:40.273 --> 40:41.973
It's peaceful up here.

40:43.806 --> 40:45.906
Don't you like how peaceful it is?

40:48.616 --> 40:49.816
[GRUNTS]

40:52.149 --> 40:53.581
No!

40:53.582 --> 40:55.115
- It's too late!
- No!

40:55.116 --> 40:56.359
Even if you knew how.

40:56.516 --> 40:59.015
- Even if you knew how.
- Mom!

40:59.016 --> 41:01.881
Listen, there's no place
in the world for us.

41:01.882 --> 41:04.661
No place they won't know
who we are or what we've done.

41:06.849 --> 41:10.137
All the gold in the world can't
wash away the mark of Cain.

41:11.449 --> 41:12.981
It'll be hard on Dad.

41:13.153 --> 41:14.477
But better in the end.

41:17.349 --> 41:18.415
I love you.

41:18.563 --> 41:21.165
This is the only gift I can give you.

41:21.616 --> 41:23.848
Will you hold us, mother?

41:23.849 --> 41:29.048
♪♪

41:29.049 --> 41:34.181
♪♪

41:34.182 --> 41:39.382
♪♪

41:40.849 --> 41:48.548
♪♪

41:48.549 --> 41:53.048
